            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sauce thickens, chop the<strong> dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add most of the<strong> chopped dill</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) to the thickened sauce</p><p>Return the <strong>browned</strong> <strong>meatballs</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 5 min further until the sauce has thickened to a gravy-like consistency – these are your <strong>Swedish-style meat-free meatballs & gravy</strong></p>",
