      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Return the pot of <strong>drained</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a low heat and add a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Mash until smooth, then season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
